<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no">
    <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection" />
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="css/shouji-css.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="js/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid hd_hb">
        <div class="hongb hongb_tu_hb">
            <img src="images/8_hongb_hb.png" />
            <p class="hb_wen1 hb_wen">恭喜您,获得了</p>
            <p class="hb_wen2 hb_too_geshu"><b>8</b>个红包</p>
            <p class="hb_wen3 hb_wen">红包活动专区内</p>
            <p class="hb_wen4 hb_wen">每消费满2元,即获得1个随机红包</p>
            <a style="top:74%;">拆红包</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $(".hongb>img").load(function () {
                var zong = $(window).height();
                var b = $(".hongb_tu_hb").height();
                if (b > zong)
                    zong = b;
                $(".hd_hb").height(zong);
                var tu = $(".hongb").height();
                //          alert(zong + ":" + tu);
                $(".hongb").css("margin-top", (zong - tu) / 2 + "px");
            })
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
